entries.content:
Fixed: Added CHAT_MODEL_CHANGED event mapping in ChatOutgoingMappers.

The event now flows:
1. UI: OptionsDropdown emits UI_EVENTS.CHAT_MODEL_CHANGED
2. Bridge: ChatOutgoingMappers maps to 'chat.model.changed.v1' bridge event
3. Extension: Needs handler for 'chat.model.changed.v1' (next step)

Added mapModelChanged() method following existing pattern (mapAgentInterrupt, mapPermissionResponse).
Registered in getMappings() array.
